body:
Why do Honor Level 5 Orbs give such little reward? Usually I get around 100 essence and 3 key fragments? Where&#039;s the incentive..?

Am I just unlucky? The first Orb gave me a sense of &quot;Woah!&quot; now I can barely squeeze out an &quot;Okay, cool...&quot;. In a competitive game where you&#039;re dealing with toxic people quite often and have to really put your all into being honorable, wouldn&#039;t it make sense to at least get a random skin shard?

